General.Name: Classic Scenic Bhd
General.Description: Classic Scenic Berhad, an investment holding company, manufactures and sells wooden picture frame moldings and wooden pallets in North America, Australia, Malaysia, and internationally. The company operates through three segments: Wooden Picture Frame Mouldings, Other Timber Products, and Property Holding. It also engages in the manufacture and sale of various timber products; and property holding and rental activities, as well as operates as a sawmilling contractor. The company was founded in 1955 and is headquartered in Rawang, Malaysia.
